msgstr "或通过环境变量："

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/cpu_ram.rst:110
msgid "**Restrictions**"
msgstr "**限制**"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/cpu_ram.rst:112
msgid "Hugepages are **not compatible with P2P mode** (``enable_p2p: true``)."
msgstr "大页 **与 P2P 模式不兼容** (``enable_p2p: true``)。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/cpu_ram.rst:113
msgid "Hugepages are **not compatible with shared memory** (``shm_name`` is set)."
msgstr "大页与 **共享内存** 不兼容（``shm_name`` 已设置）。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/cpu_ram.rst:114
msgid ""
"On non-CUDA platforms, hugepages are not supported. Regular allocation "
"will be used as fallback."
msgstr "在非CUDA平台上，不支持大页。将使用常规分配作为后备。"

